  "text": "In the beginning, let us observe the actual efficiency of the proposed emergent migration strategies tackling three problems of varying difficulty: eil51, berlin52, and kroB200. In this section, the emergent behavior of the ants is evaluated, and the efficacy of such a dynamically adapting metaheuristic is compared to the classic ACO and one of its best socio-cognitive versions (egoWithoutBad from [CITATION_1] containing 60% EC, 20% AC, 20% GC, and 0% BC ants).",
